  "detailed_description": "<br><strong>From now on, you can have an exciting PVP online points duel with other online players!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Devil's Game</h2>Stepping into the dimly lit underground Club, you will play with the devil and experience a thrilling game of Shot Roulette.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006980/extras/53d9cd883d8fe484fb4f092d9c51f94b.poster.avif?t=1724639043\" width=600 height=283 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006980/extras/53d9cd883d8fe484fb4f092d9c51f94b.webm?t=1724639043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Mystery Box of Your's</h2>Each time you open the mysterious box, you will obtain different item, rewriting the fate of life and death in roulette.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006980/extras/df9228f058d4a011933dc8c97b20ffc3.poster.avif?t=1724639043\" width=600 height=283 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006980/extras/df9228f058d4a011933dc8c97b20ffc3.webm?t=1724639043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Exciting Game of Roulette</h2>In this tense and exciting roulette, every choice you make is crucial and life and death hang in the balance.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006980/extras/f5e8b34b85187d2aa13ab0f3aab9d513.poster.avif?t=1724639043\" width=600 height=283 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006980/extras/f5e8b34b85187d2aa13ab0f3aab9d513.webm?t=1724639043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Bet From Hell</h2>Accept the call from hell, bet bravely, challenge the unknown, become the undisputed winner of Roulette Club, and reveal the ultimate secret of this mysterious adventure!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006980/extras/743a38ffa078eb1a44d3e0d037b816da.poster.avif?t=1724639043\" width=600 height=283 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3006980/extras/743a38ffa078eb1a44d3e0d037b816da.webm?t=1724639043\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
